      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or an ultra-budget ride? Here's your chance! We'll be straight with you \u2014 this vehicle is in poor condition, meaning it has significant wear, mechanical issues, and cosmetic damage that will need attention. It's not a daily driver for everyone, but for a handy buyer or someone who loves a good fixer-upper, there's real potential here. Priced accordingly at $5,500 to reflect its current state honestly. Come take a look and see if it's the right project for you!",
